														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3816577">
									

<p>Here is a brief explanation of the general plot so far:</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Spoilers&nbsp;aweigh!</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">squawk</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>By some mechanism, the deity Thoth uses the Doomsday Clock (SCP-3662) as a conduit to transmit a stolen Avian meme complex (referenced in SPC-507) into all human minds. As a result, humans become less human-like and more bird-like (Join the Flock).</p>
<p><strong>How does the Foundation know it was him?</strong> Because they detected him using a specialized satellite (SCP-3296) that detects reality-bending threats such as evil deities.</p>
<p><strong>Why was he able to do what he did?</strong> Because the Foundation messed up big time and trapped Earth's resident Christian deity into a Christmas movie (SCP-3362).</p>
<p><strong>And who is here to clean up the mess and save the day?</strong> MTF-Eta-4 &quot;Begone Thoth&quot; of the Avian Division (SCP-3095) and MFT CHARYBDIS of the Shark Punching Centre (SPC-507).</p>
<p>Story to be continued in Act II!</p>
</div>
